澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻 综合报道中国国内疫情逐渐好转，但这个时候全球各地却不断拉响警报，新冠肺炎全球风险级别由高风险提升至非常高。
The roar news reports a gradual improvement in China, but as the world alarms, the global risk of pneumonia has risen from high to very high.
据世界卫生组织官网报道，世卫组织总干事谭德塞2日表示，中国的新冠肺炎病例数量在持续下降，在过去24小时内，中国境外报告的病例数几乎是中国境内的9倍。
The number of new cases of pneumonia in China has continued to decline, with nearly nine times the number of cases reported outside China in the past 24 hours, WHO official Web site reported.
世卫组织发布的最新一期新冠肺炎情况每日报告显示，截至欧洲中部时间3月2日10时(北京时间17时)，中国境外确诊新冠肺炎8774例，死亡128例。
According to the latest WHO daily report on pneumonia, 8,774 new cases of pneumonia and 128 deaths had been confirmed outside China as of 1000 CET (1700 hours Beijing time).
钟南山担心的事情发生了此前，钟南山院士曾表示，新冠肺炎疫情在国外迅速蔓延，中国存在从输出病例变为输入病例的可能性。
Zhong's concern comes after academicians in Zhong Nan Shan said the outbreak of pneumonia was spreading rapidly abroad and that there was a possibility that China could move from exporting cases to importing cases.
而钟南山院士所担心的事情正在陆续出现。
And the concerns of the academicians are beginning to emerge.
截至目前，浙江、宁夏、北京、广东都陆续通报了境外输入病例。
So far, Zhejiang, Ningxia, Beijing and Guangdong have all reported overseas cases.
浙江新增7例境外输入病例3月3日，浙江省公布新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情情况，新增境外（意大利）输入性确诊病例7例。
Seven new cases of coronavirus pneumonia were reported in Zhejiang Province on March 3, adding 7 confirmed cases of imported coronavirus from abroad.
该7例病例与首例境外输入病例王某某为密切接触者，在意大利贝加莫同一家餐厅工作，8人一直生活在意大利，无湖北武汉接触史。
The 7 cases were in close contact with Wang, who worked in the same restaurant in Bergamo, Italy. Eight people have lived in Italy and have no history of contact with Wuhan, Hubei Province.
患者蒋某，男，34岁，户籍青田县瓯南街道；患者王某，男，29岁，户籍青田县瓯南街道；患者叶某某，男，36岁，户籍青田县瓯南街道；患者陈某某，男，23岁，户籍青田县油竹街道；患者叶某某，女，32岁，户籍青田县油竹街道；患者章某某，男，33岁，户籍青田县油竹街道。
Patient Jiang Mou, male, 34 years old, Ounan Street, Qingtian County, household registration; patient Wang Mou, male, 29, Ounan street, Qingtian County, household registration; patient, male, 23-year-old, Yuzhu street, hukou Qingtian county; patient Ye, female, 32, Yuzhu street, hukou Qingtian county; patient Zhang, male, 33, Yuzhu street, Qingtian county, household registration.
6人均在意大利贝加莫从事餐饮服务工作。
All six worked in the catering service in Bergamo, Italy.
2月26日，6人一同乘坐SU2415H航班从米兰到莫斯科。
On 26 February, six people were travelling together on flight SU2415H from Milan to Moscow.
2月27日，从莫斯科乘坐SU206H航班到达上海浦东国际机场。
February 27, from Moscow on SU206H flight to Shanghai Pudong International Airport.
2月28日，6人包车进入青田，当即落实隔离观察措施。
On 28 February, six persons chartered into Qingtian, where they immediately put in place quarantine observation measures.
3月2日，经检测，6人新冠肺炎核酸检测均呈阳性，现正在定点医院隔离治疗。
On 2 March, six people tested positive for Nucleic Acid (Nucleic Acid) for New Crown Pneumonia, and are now undergoing isolation treatment at the designated hospital.
患者叶某，男，34岁，户籍青田县三溪口街道，与首例病例为密切接触者，在意大利贝加莫同一家餐厅工作。
The patient, Ye Mou, male, aged 34, works in the same restaurant in Bergamo, Italy, in close contact with the first patient, Sanxikou Street, Qingtian county, Italy.
2月28日，患者乘坐LH0273航班从意大利到德国。
On 28 February, the patient travelled from Italy to Germany on flight LH0273.
2月29日，从德国乘坐CA0936航班到达上海浦东机场。
On 29 February, it arrived at Shanghai Pudong Airport on flight CA0936 from Germany.
2月29日，患者包车进入青田，当即落实隔离观察措施。
On 29 February, the patient chartered into Qingtian and immediately put in place quarantine observation measures.
3月2日，新冠肺炎核酸检测呈阳性，现正在定点医院隔离治疗。
On 2 March, Nucleic Acid Nucleic Acid (Nucleic Acid) test was positive, and isolation treatment is being ordered at the hospital.
深圳新增1例境外输入病例据广东卫健委2日消息，截至3月1日24时，广东全省累计报告新冠肺炎确诊病例1350例，累计出院1034例，累计死亡7例。
As of 2400 hours on March 1, a total of 1,350 confirmed cases of New Crown Pneumonia had been reported in Guangdong Province, with a total of 1,034 cases of discharge, with a cumulative total of 7 deaths, the Guangdong Health Commission reported Wednesday.
3月1日当天全省新增确诊病例1例，为深圳报告1例境外输入病例。
March 1, the province of a new confirmed case, Shenzhen reported a case of foreign importation.
新增出院25例，3例为重型病例治愈出院，其余为普通型或轻型病例治愈出院。
Twenty-five new cases were discharged from hospital, three cases were cured in heavy cases and the rest were cured in normal or light cases.
无疑似病例。
No suspected cases.
有874名密切接触者正在接受医学观察。
There are 874 close contacts under medical observation.
宁夏发现2例境外输入病例3月1日，宁夏应对新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情工作指挥部发布最新全区新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情通报。
Ningxia found 2 cases of imported cases March 1, Ningxia should respond to the new coronavirus pneumonia epidemic command issued the latest report on the new coronavirus pneumonia in the region.
截至2月29日24时，全区累计报告确诊病例73例，累计出院病例69例。
As of 2400 hours on February 29, the region had reported a cumulative total of 73 confirmed cases and 69 cumulative cases of discharge.
现有疑似病例5例（较28日增加1例）。
There were 5 suspected cases (an increase of 1 case over 28 days).
澎湃新闻（www.thepaper.cn）记者注意到，这73例确诊病例中，有两例新冠肺炎确诊病例确诊前刚从伊朗德黑兰经俄罗斯莫斯科转机回国。
Correspondents at thepper.cn noted that two of the 73 confirmed cases had just returned from Tehran, Iran, via Moscow, Russia, before being confirmed.
据宁夏卫健委宣传处工作人员介绍，目前两人均在宁夏第四人民医院集中救治。
According to Ningxia Wei health promotion office staff, at present two people in Ningxia Fourth People's Hospital concentrated treatment.
北京新增2例境外输入病例2月29日，北京市报告2例自伊朗入境的新冠肺炎确诊病例，均为2月26日宁夏确诊病例丁某某在伊朗期间的密切接触者。
BEIJING, Feb. 29 (Xinhua) -- Two confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia from Iran were reported in Beijing on February 29, both close contacts while Ding was confirmed in Iran on February 26.
怎样防控海外疫情输入？3月1日，国务院联防联控机制新闻发布会上，海关总署卫生检疫司司长林伟表示，海关对所有出入境人员实施百分之百的查验健康申报，全面开展体温监测筛查，严密实施医学巡查。
On March 1, the Health and Quarantine Director-General of the General Administration of Customs, Lin Wei, said at a press conference to prevent the importation of foreign epidemic diseases.
对于这些查验中发现的有症状的，或者是来自于疫情比较严重的国家或地区，或者是接触过确诊病例、疑似病例的人员，严格实施流行病学排查、医学排查以及实验室检测进行排查。
Epidemiological screening, medical screening and laboratory tests are carried out to detect symptomatic cases found in these examinations, either from countries or regions with more severe epidemics or from persons who have been exposed to confirmed cases or suspected cases.
也有专家提醒，疫情防控阻击战尚未结束。
Experts also warned that the prevention and control of the epidemic is not over.
无论您身处国内或境外，鉴于乘坐飞机等公共交通工具感染病毒的风险较大，居家是最好的防护。
Whether you are inside or outside the country, your home is the best protection, given the higher risk of contracting the virus by public transportation such as air travel.
为了您和他人健康，请务必继续保持警惕，加强自我防范，慎重决定出行计划。
For your health and the health of others, you must continue to be vigilant, strengthen self-defense, carefully decided travel plans.
如有发热、呼吸道感染、腹泻等症状，要及时到二级及以上医疗机构的发热门诊就诊。
If there is fever, respiratory tract infection, diarrhea and other symptoms, to timely access to the heating clinic of the second and higher medical institutions.
